{"tid":1568883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑黨鐵請左保安捉人跳閘","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:08:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:21:39.000Z","uid":251192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"50736d9e42a7255a238306e4c88d2a8b875ac6e1","tid":1568883,"uid":251192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:08:58.000Z","msg":"小弟今日係南昌站見到六七個白衣保安同個黃衣傾嘢傾到好認真咁，就去偷聽下，好似係見到有人跳閘，仲話要巡吓個廁所。<br />\n<br />\n啲白衣專企係閘機前，𥄫到實一實。<br />\n<br />\n咁南昌呢排賣樓agent入曬站係閘機前面去sell樓盤<br />\n，但係啲白衣保安又唔趕班agent走，佢地都企係閘機度全日喇。<br />\n<br />\n小弟問左個黃衣呢樣嘢，佢話 <strong>呢啲嘢唔方便透露太多</strong> <br />\n<br />\n小弟懷疑黨鐵特登請左批廢中保安黎捉跳閘，各位手足小心啲喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eWfJPSu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeWfJPSu.png&h=b1578027&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kL3n5qP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkL3n5qP.png&h=91c014b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"904fdf6f626ba1a130c224349827246dc0c01028","tid":1568883,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"Amazon文具助養計劃：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AMAZON0101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAMAZON0101&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSugAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=606c269b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AMAZON0101</a><br />\n<br />\n小朋友有需要補充請過黎shopping<br />\n家長亦可提供sponsor🙏🏻"},{"pid":"25b559f1c62e3dc43af610194e024376ab54b4fe","tid":1568883,"uid":109923,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:11:09.000Z","msg":"企定定望實閘機你都只係懷疑？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b613c18146bb3bd83ac51e7f18762beadf027600","tid":1568883,"uid":251192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:11:11.000Z","msg":"自推 1"},{"pid":"63f7ba1cd801e28619cd47ae9666cabb3a1b5def","tid":1568883,"uid":251192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"